<L>__{exterior san francisco airport night}
<A>__{several small planes are parked on the tarmac. mother superior and the nuns are arguing with the manager of the airport, a grouchy guy in grease stained overalls.}
<C>__{manager}
<D>__{fifteen hundred for the run to vegas. rock bottom.}
<C>__{mary patrick}
<D>__{but we don't have fifteen hundred!}
<C>__{mary robert}
<D>__{we're nuns!}
<A>__{the manager starts back toward his office.}
<C>__{manager}
<D>__{can't help you. no exceptions.}
<C>__{mother superior}
<D>__{young man!}
<A>__{the voice has a powerful ring of authority to it, and the manager looks around.}
<C>__{manager}
<D>__{what?}
